reviews.text: A public housing estate located next to Sheung Shui Station
Quick charging station for EV drivers, next to Sheung Shui MTR, very convenient to cross border!
Well, never did like the "Link" at all, busy place cost its builder n blocked in residential area.
It is OK, but food variety is not good enough, especially not many choice of good restaurants.
